                  <summary>Ziq Chants, መጽሐፈ፡ ዚቅ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="110v" facs="003">Fols 1r–110v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1979Mashaf">Maṣḥafa ziq</title>
